{"tid":1800171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［CelPay］加密貨幣PayMe式應用","createTime":"2019-12-27T14:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T14:51:00.000Z","uid":191531,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8c1c2d860eebdb0ccad430aec9ca4c2fa9caa2fc","tid":1800171,"uid":191531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:17:59.000Z","msg":"CelPay，係Celsius Network個app入面嘅其中一個功能。<strong>一句講晒，佢就係加密貨幣嘅PayMe，send條link/喺app入面撳兩撳就比倒錢人。</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n優點：<br />\n+ 簡單<br />\n+ 英國公司（i.e. 非大陸/香港公司）<br />\n<br />\n缺點：<br />\n- 要KYC（i.e. 身份認證）<br />\n- 中心化<br />\n- 公司歷史短（2017創業）<br />\n<br />\n喺度講CelPay主要係貪佢簡化咗加密貨幣嘅比錢/收錢過程；個人認爲簡單化係打長遠經濟戰：快速普及化加密貨幣、減少依賴港幣嘅關鍵一環；Celsius Network嘅其他功能（e.g. 存款利息、法幣借貸）有興趣先再討論<br />\n<br />\n如果有高手識其他更好嘅applications請不吝賜教<br />\n<br />\n無推廣連結：<a href=\"https://celsius.network/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcelsius.network%2F&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPB6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=d719eba3\" target=\"_blank\">https://celsius.network/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b33affb269e1446d09cf6ad94e427a21a5bd02d","tid":1800171,"uid":81862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:19:25.000Z","msg":"幫你推 想知點用"},{"pid":"5bfe84f7795357976b3e02c54713ec41d02fa7c3","tid":1800171,"uid":81862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:19:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ea69cf2259bc74f2c94f23f972372f32a22ae9bd","tid":1800171,"uid":191531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b33affb269e1446d09cf6ad94e427a21a5bd02d","tid":1800171,"uid":81862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:19:25.000Z","msg":"幫你推 想知點用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:51:00.000Z","msg":"單純講比錢人的話，揀貨幣揀金額再揀收款人 / gen條link比收款人就搞掂<br />\n官網CelPay頁面：<a href=\"https://celsius.network/celpay/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcelsius.network%2Fcelpay%2F&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPB6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=5a387018\" target=\"_blank\">https://celsius.network/celpay/</a>（無咩嘢睇因爲無咩複雜性）<br />\n<br />\n如果係講一開始點樣入錢，有兩個方法：<br />\n1. 喺app入面透過同佢哋合作嘅公司Moon Pay用信用卡買你想要嘅嗰隻加密貨幣；或者<br />\n2. 透過佢存款嘅wallet address由你自己wallet / 自己用開嘅加密貨幣交易所轉入你嘅資產<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得 (1) 比較適合新手用家，(2) 比較適合有用開/有興趣研究加密貨幣嘅用家（複雜性高啲，但係買賣手續費普遍低啲同流動性大啲）"}]}